snippet.title: Super Galaxy Ranger Luna 64 - N64 Nostalga In Space!
snippet.description:
Evocative of the grand ol' days of the Nintendo 64, this rough cut gem does a fantastic job of emulating it's inspirations! While Luna can't aim to saver her life, I really enjoyed this and might just go back for a little more!

Play It Yourself: https://gamejolt.com/games/luna64/259614

Join Me On Twitter: https://twitter.com/ReallyCoalFire

Subscribe for more CoalFire!
Outro music by Chad Atkins: https://soundcloud.com/chad-atkins
